Entoning lelo ooitoreisho


1  Entoning pooki tung'ani oitoreisho. Amu meetae enkitoria neme Enkai eing'uaa, ore lelo ooatae naa Enkai naitasheyie. 
2  Neaku ore ake oloibooyo enkitoria te ngogong'i ina naa Enkai naitasheyie, ore lelo ooibooyo te ngogong'i naa ate eyaki enkiguana. 
3  Amu meiture laitoriak oltung'ani lo lkuaak supat, kake eiture olo ltorrono. Iyieu iyie nimiaata enkuretisho te ilo oitoreisho? Taasa naa isupati, naa itum errepet te ninye. 
4  Amu osinka le Nkai ninye likiyaki isupati. Kake ore ake pee ias intorrok, tureisho, amu menapita ninye olalem pesho; osinka le Nkai ninye oitabaiki engoro enye ilo oas intorrok. 
5  Ore enkaraki ina entoning naa, neme enkaraki ake naa iurere engoro e Nkai kake te nkaraki oltoilo lo ltau. 
6   Naa enkaraki ake ina sii pee ilakilaka kodi, amu ore lelo ooitoreisho naa laisiaayiak le Nkai ooirrita ina bae. 
7  Enchoo lelo pooki nena naairirikino ninche, enchoo kodi ilooishori kodi, ninchosho esotore lelo le sotore, entureita ninchosho enkanyit lelo ooiririkino enkanyit.

Enyorrata oo lalashera


8  Emiaatayie esile oltung'ani hoo obo, ae neme ene nyorrata maate; amu ore ilo onyor ole latia enye neitabayie nkitanapat. 
9   Ore nena kitanapat naajo, “Miloloito, miaar metua, mipurrisho, ming'uar” o kulie ake kitanapat, naa kulo rorei ooitululung. “Tonyorra ole latia ino anaa eninyor kewan.” 
10  Meitaas enyorrata ole latia entorrono; enkaraki ina paa enyorrata enkitabaroto oo nkitanapat.

Etinyikua enkolong e Kristo


11  Ore etii nena niyiololo sii aajo kaa saa ena nchere etabawua tukul enkata pee iputunyenye aaing'uaa injo. Amu taata etataanikia iyiook enjeunoto alang enapa kata pee kinteru aairuk; 
12  etinyikayie enkewarie, etaa ekenyu. Ematuburukushu naa isiaaitin e naimin emaishopo masaa e wang'an; 
13  emaitobirai ate anaa loopuo dama, neme te sikar o te merai, neme te malmalisho oo ng'uarrat torrok, neme too nkitarrikinot o to lom. 
14  Kake enchopo Olaitoriani Yesu Kristo, naa emintoki ake aaisho osesen erishata, metaa nena ake naayieu intabayaya.

